data.description: 6-acre wooded retreat with a modern twist! The spacious 3824 sq ft of living space includes 5 bedrooms and 3 baths and offers a versatile floor plan with plenty of space to live, work, and play. The centerpiece of the home is undoubtedly the stunning, updated white kitchen which has 2 dishwashers, custom cabinetry, a farmhouse sink, and stunning white quartz countertops. The formal dining room plus main floor living room and family room (both with fireplaces!) make this the perfect home to gather and entertain. Walk to the Kiwanis Family Park Greenway which leads to a large playground and splash pad, a haven for family fun and recreation. Also just minutes to downtown Sanford with an easy commute to Fort Liberty or up US 1 to Raleigh. Be sure to request the long list of updates and features, including newer roof and HVAC.
